I use combo of #lowcarb + #keto; moving more #carnivore now.

Calorie deficit + IF didn’t work for my body—spent a decade fighting insulin resistance, kept gaining.

Counted macros—v high protein, some fats, MINIMAL CARBS key for me.

Now mostly protein + intuitive eating.🙌🏻

✅ Keep it SIMPLE
✅ #LowCarb/minimal sugars
✅ Focus on Protein
✅ Eat when hungry, not on schedule, unless fasting
✅ Prep ahead/buy prepared foods to stay on track
